WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
&lt;h2&gt;The Leak&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;On March 26, 2026, a CMS misconfiguration at Anthropic

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
exposed roughly 3,000 unpublished blog assets — including a draft

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
post describing Claude Mythos, a new model tier above Opus.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Security researchers Roy Paz (LayerX) and Alexandre Pauwels (Cambridge) found

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
the exposed data store. Fortune broke the story.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What Is Capybara?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Capybara

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
is Anthropic's new fourth model tier, positioned above Opus. Claude

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Mythos is the first model in this tier. Anthropic calls

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
it "a step change" and "the most capable we've built

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:36.000
to date," with dramatically higher scores in coding, reasoning, and

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
cybersecurity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Cybersecurity Concerns&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The draft warns Mythos is "far ahead of any

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
other AI model in cyber capabilities" — able to find

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
and exploit software vulnerabilities at machine speed. This triggered a

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
major cybersecurity stock selloff: CrowdStrike -7%, Palo Alto Networks -6%,

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
Tenable -11%, Zscaler -4.5%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;IPO Plans&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bloomberg reported the same day that

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Anthropic is targeting an October 2026 IPO, potentially raising 0B+.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
The company is valued at ~80B after a 0B February

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
funding round, running at 4B annualized revenue. The timing has

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
fueled skepticism about whether the leak was truly accidental.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Open Questions&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;When

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.000
will Mythos be available via API? What will pricing look

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
like? Will cybersecurity concerns trigger regulation? And was this leak

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.200
intentional pre-IPO marketing?&lt;/p&gt;
